- Designs have to be at least 4000x5323 pixel and 300 dpi resolution. (Can be bigger yes) The design has to be this resolution, not the mock up/preview
- You have to follow Discord and Twitch TOS.
- No copyrighted material, fair use allowed. (example: No BTTV/FFZ emotes, no company logos, no "googled images". (unless you show me that you have rights to them.))
- You can put a watermark over your design, if you want.
- No transparency effect (The final design has to be 100% opacity)
- Follow the template attached to this message. (https://i.imgur.com/55J7OuM.png / https://i.imgur.com/Llij6dE.png)
- You can create your free mock up on these websites: https://bit.ly/2ZZw9NC or https://bit.ly/2NJg3Fz or anywhere else.
